sentences.sentence: She has found eBay an ideal way to sell her $50 cocktail and rockabilly swing dresses and did $700, 000 in sales last year.

sentences.sentence: If you play bluegrass, rockabilly or baroque music, you owe it to yourself to play on a true, full set of all of gut strings.

sentences.sentence: I'm a simple guy who likes simple things, and to me the sound of blues, punk rock, rockabilly, and funk are simple and pure expression_r_r_rs.
sentences.translation: 我是一个很简单的人，喜欢简单的事情，布鲁斯，庞克摇滚乐，乡村摇滚乐，乡土爵士乐，在我看来都是简单纯净的表达方式。
